                        <li>Guidance on security, architecture, and implementation</li>
                        <li>Support with presentation, documentation, and technical polish</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="mt-3 italic">The goal of Stage 2 is to help teams deliver solutions that could genuinely be piloted or deployed within government.</p>
